Package chat.web.bean

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdministrationBean
    This managed bean supports the operations and UI components of the administration page.
    ChatBean
    This managed bean supports the operations and UI components of the chat page.
    ChatRoomManager
    This managed bean manages the HTTP sessions, web-socket sessions, and chat room congregations for users of the chat room application.
    HistoryBean
    This managed bean supports the operations and UI components of the conversation history page.
    LobbyBean
    This managed bean supports the operations and UI components of the lobby page.
    MessageDispatcher
    This managed bean relays messages between chat room users.
    RegistrationBean
    This managed bean supports the components and operations of the registration page.
    UserBean
    This managed bean handles the chat room user data to support the faces pages.
